<chapter id="jdiameter">

	<title>&THIS.PLATFORM; Diameter Stack</title>

	<para>The &THIS.PLATFORM; Diameter Stack is the core component of the presented Diameter solution. It performs all necessary tasks to allow user interact with
		Diameter network. It manages state of diameter peers and allows to route messages between them. For details please refer to <ulink url="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3588">RFC 3588</ulink>.</para>
	<para>Currently the &THIS.PLATFORM; Diameter Stack supports the following application sessions:</para>
	<itemizedlist>
		<listitem>
			<para>Base</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Credit Control Application (CCA)</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Sh</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Ro</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Rf</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Cx/Dx</para>
		</listitem>
	</itemizedlist>
	

